<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Zoophagical distaste -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Dislikes.label>不喜食兽</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Dislikes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn dislikes having animals as prey. Maybe it can't bear to see its fuzzy friends imperiled, maybe it thinks cannibalism is the true way, maybe it just doesn't like to get dirt and fur all over its tongue. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Dislikes.description>这个角色不喜欢把动物当作猎物。也许是舍不得那些毛茸茸的朋友遭殃，也许是觉得同类相食才是正道，也许单纯就是不喜欢舌头沾上一嘴泥和毛。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Dislikes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Zoophagical taste -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Likes.label>喜食兽肉</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Likes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn likes having animals as prey. It's what most sapient life's been doing already for thousands of years; why stop now, especially when they squirm so wildly? -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Likes.description>这个角色喜欢把动物当作猎物。毕竟智慧生物捕食动物已经干了几千年了，何必现在改口呢——更何况它们挣扎起来那么带劲？</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Likes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Zoophagical ambivalence -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Neutral.label>食兽随缘</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Neutral.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn doesn't mind having animals as prey, but doesn't prefer them either. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Neutral.description>这个角色不排斥把动物当猎物，但也没有特别的偏好。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Neutral.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Zoophagical obsession -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Obsessed.label>痴迷兽肉</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Obsessed.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn adores having animals as prey. Never let it watch your pets. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Obsessed.description>这个角色对把动物当作猎物痴迷不已。千万别让它盯上你的宠物。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Obsessed.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Zoophagical revulsion -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Refuses.label>拒食兽肉</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Refuses.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn hates having animals as prey and will never willingly consume them. It would sooner hunt the beast down, skin it, butcher it, cook it, and eat it, all on its own, than swallow it whole. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Refuses.description>这个角色厌恶把动物当猎物，绝不会主动吞食它们。比起活吞，它宁愿亲手把猎物猎杀、剥皮、肢解、烹饪，再一口一口吃下去——至少那样更体面。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Animals_Refuses.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Anthropophagical distaste -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Dislikes.label>不喜食人</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Dislikes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn dislikes having its fellow sapient beings as prey. Maybe it's too much like cannibalism; maybe it's self-conscious about its insides. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Dislikes.description>这个角色不喜欢把其他智慧生物当作猎物。也许是太像同类相食了，也许是对自己肚子里那点事有些介意。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Dislikes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Anthropophagical taste (cannibal) -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Likes_Cannibal.label>喜食人肉（食人者）</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Likes_Cannibal.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn likes having its fellow sapient beings as prey; even fatally, as an extension of its cannibalistic tendencies. People are tasty! And clean, usually. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Likes_Cannibal.description>这个角色喜欢把其他智慧生物当作猎物——哪怕后果致命，也不过是其食人倾向的延伸罢了。人肉很美味！而且通常挺干净的。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Likes_Cannibal.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Anthropophagical taste (endo) -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Likes_NotCannibal.label>喜食人肉（安全向）</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Likes_NotCannibal.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn likes having its fellow sapient beings as prey, so long as it's safe. Fatal vore, on the other hand, is no different from regular old butcher-and-chew cannibalism. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Likes_NotCannibal.description>这个角色喜欢把其他智慧生物当作猎物——只要安全无事就好。至于致命的吞食嘛，那跟老一套的屠宰咀嚼式食人也没什么区别。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Likes_NotCannibal.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Anthropophagical ambivalence -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Neutral.label>食人随缘</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Neutral.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn doesn't mind having its fellow sapient beings as prey, fatal or otherwise, but doesn't prefer them either. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Neutral.description>这个角色不排斥把其他智慧生物当猎物——无论是否致命——但也没有特别的偏好。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Neutral.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Anthropophagical obsession (cannibal) -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Obsessed_Cannibal.label>痴迷食人（食人者）</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Obsessed_Cannibal.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn adores having its fellow sapient beings as prey; even fatally, as an extension of its cannibalistic tendencies. Humanoid meat tastes best alive and kicking. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Obsessed_Cannibal.description>这个角色对把其他智慧生物当作猎物痴迷不已——哪怕后果致命，也不过是其食人倾向的极致体现。人形生物的肉，还是活蹦乱跳的时候最美味。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Obsessed_Cannibal.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Anthropophagical obsession (endo) -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Obsessed_NotCannibal.label>痴迷食人（安全向）</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Obsessed_NotCannibal.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn adores having its fellow sapient beings as prey, so long as it's safe. The dark side of vore does tempt it though, with all these delicious, filling preythings... -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Obsessed_NotCannibal.description>这个角色对把其他智慧生物当作猎物痴迷不已——只要安全无事就好。不过，面对那些美味又饱腹的猎物，吞食的黑暗面也时时在诱惑着它……</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Obsessed_NotCannibal.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Anthropophagical revulsion -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Refuses.label>拒食人肉</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Refuses.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn hates having its fellow sapient beings as prey and will never willingly consume them. It's a perversion of the natural order, cannibalistic or not. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Refuses.description>这个角色厌恶把其他智慧生物当猎物，绝不会主动吞食它们。无论是否涉及同类相食，这都是一种对自然秩序的扭曲。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Humanoids_Refuses.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Entomophagical distaste -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Dislikes.label>不喜食虫</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Dislikes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn dislikes having live bugs as prey. It has a list of places bugs should not be, and one of those places is "alive and crawling around inside its body". -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Dislikes.description>这个角色不喜欢把活生生的虫子当猎物。它心里有一份"虫子不该待的地方"清单，其中一条就是"活着在它体内爬来爬去"。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Dislikes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Entomophagical taste -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Likes.label>喜食虫肉</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Likes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn enjoys having live bugs as prey. Its taste for chewing chitin extends to raw and cooked bug meat, too. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Likes.description>这个角色喜欢把活生生的虫子当猎物。它咀嚼甲壳素的喜好也延伸到了生虫肉和熟虫肉上。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Likes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Entomophagical ambivalence -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Neutral.label>食虫随缘</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Neutral.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn doesn't mind having live bugs as prey, but doesn't prefer them either. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Neutral.description>这个角色不排斥把活虫子当猎物，但也没有特别的偏好。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Neutral.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Entomophagical obsession -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Obsessed.label>痴迷虫肉</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Obsessed.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn adores having live bugs as prey. Its whole body may as well be a hive. Furthermore, its taste for chewing chitin extends to raw and cooked bug meat, too. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Obsessed.description>这个角色对把活虫子当猎物痴迷不已。它的整个身体简直就是一个虫巢。此外，它咀嚼甲壳素的喜好也延伸到了生虫肉和熟虫肉上。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Obsessed.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Entomophagical revulsion -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Refuses.label>拒食虫肉</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Refuses.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn hates having live bugs as prey and will never willingly consume them. The very thought makes its skin crawl. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Refuses.description>这个角色厌恶把活虫子当猎物，绝不会主动吞食它们。光是想想就浑身起鸡皮疙瘩。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Insectoids_Refuses.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Mechanophagical distaste -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Dislikes.label>不喜机械</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Dislikes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn dislikes having mechanoids as prey. They're cold and angry and don't exactly feel great to swallow. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Dislikes.description>这个角色不喜欢把机械体当猎物。它们又冷又暴躁，吞下去的感觉实在不怎么样。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Dislikes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Mechanophagical taste -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Likes.label>喜食机械</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Likes.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn likes having mechanoids as prey. It proves the flesh is stronger than the machine, or something. That doesn't necessarily equate to the digestive strength to churn a mechanoid into food, but it's something. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Likes.description>这个角色喜欢把机械体当猎物。这大概能证明血肉比机械更强之类的吧。当然，喜欢归喜欢，胃里有没有能耐把机械体化成食物就是另一回事了——但至少态度摆出来了。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Likes.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Mechanophagical ambivalence -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Neutral.label>机械随缘</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Neutral.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn doesn't mind having mechanoids as prey, but doesn't prefer them either. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Neutral.description>这个角色不排斥把机械体当猎物，但也没有特别的偏好。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Neutral.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Mechanophagical obsession -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Obsessed.label>痴迷机械</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Obsessed.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn adores having mechanoids as prey. It has the munchies for metal, a taste for titanium and steel. That doesn't necessarily equate to the digestive strength to churn a mechanoid into food, but it's something. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Obsessed.description>这个角色对把机械体当猎物痴迷不已。它就是对金属有食欲，对钛和钢情有独钟。当然，痴迷归痴迷，胃里有没有能耐把机械体化成食物就是另一回事了——但至少热情是满满的。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Obsessed.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Mechanophagical revulsion -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Refuses.label>拒食机械</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Refuses.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn hates having mechanoids as prey and will never willingly consume them. It absolutely does not want to put hundreds of angry pounds' worth of sharp edges, moving parts, and cold steel directly into its body. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Refuses.description>这个角色厌恶把机械体当猎物，绝不会主动吞食它们。它绝对不想把好几百斤的锋利棱角、活动部件和冰冷钢铁直接塞进自己身体里。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_DietaryPreference_Predator_Mechanoids_Refuses.description>
  
</LanguageData>